<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Concrete Beats Clever — RyanrealAF</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Space+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --ink: #0e0c0a;
    --paper: #f0ece3;
    --warm: #c8a96e;
    --rust: #b85c38;
    --ash: #6b6460;
    --ghost: #d4cfc6;
    --cement: #3a3530;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: default;
  }

  /* GRAIN OVERLAY */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.08'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    opacity: 0.45;
    mix-blend-mode: overlay;
  }

  /* HEADER / HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 0 6vw 8vh;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 70% 30%, rgba(200, 169, 110, 0.12) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 20% 80%, rgba(184, 92, 56, 0.08) 0%, transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(175deg, #1a1712 0%, #0e0c0a 50%, #090807 100%);
  }

  .hero-alley-light {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10%;
    right: 8%;
    width: 3px;
    height: 70%;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 0%, rgba(200,169,110,0.6) 20%, rgba(200,169,110,0.15) 70%, transparent 100%);
    filter: blur(8px);
    animation: flicker 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .hero-alley-light::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 15%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(200,169,110,0.25) 0%, transparent 70%);
    filter: blur(20px);
  }

  @keyframes flicker {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    47% { opacity: 1; }
    48% { opacity: 0.7; }
    49% { opacity: 1; }
    85% { opacity: 1; }
    86% { opacity: 0.8; }
    87% { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--warm);
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.2s;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(4.5rem, 14vw, 13rem);
    line-height: 0.88;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--paper);
    position: relative;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.4s;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .hero-title span {
    display: block;
    color: var(--warm);
  }

  .hero-title .title-stroke {
    -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--paper);
    color: transparent;
  }

  .hero-byline {
    margin-top: 2.4rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.7s;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .hero-byline-line {
    height: 1px;
    width: 60px;
    background: var(--warm);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .hero-byline-text {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ash);
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
    color: var(--warm);
    opacity: 0.85;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.9s;
    opacity: 0;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* SCROLL INDICATOR */
  .scroll-cue {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 3vh;
    left: 6vw;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 1.2s;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .scroll-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--warm);
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.4); }
  }

  .scroll-text {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ash);
  }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--warm), transparent);
    opacity: 0.2;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* SONIC BRIEF */
  .sonic-brief {
    background: #12100e;
    padding: 5vh 6vw;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.1);
  }

  .sonic-brief-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .sonic-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--warm);
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .sonic-text {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
    color: var(--ghost);
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  /* LYRICS SECTION */
  .lyrics-container {
    padding: 8vh 6vw;
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  .section-block {
    margin-bottom: 6vh;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }

  .section-block.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .section-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }

  .section-tag-bracket {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 1.5vw, 1rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--warm);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .section-tag-detail {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ash);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .tag-pip {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--rust);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .lyric-lines {
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .lyric-line {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: clamp(0.82rem, 1.6vw, 1rem);
    line-height: 2;
    color: var(--paper);
    opacity: 0.88;
    display: block;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .lyric-line:hover {
    opacity: 1;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .lyric-line.adlib {
    color: var(--ash);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.8em;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-left: 1.2rem;
    margin-top: -0.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .lyric-gap {
    display: block;
    height: 1.2rem;
  }

  /* HOOK — special treatment */
  .section-block.is-hook .lyric-lines {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--warm);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-block.is-hook .lyric-line {
    color: var(--paper);
    opacity: 0.95;
    font-size: clamp(0.88rem, 1.7vw, 1.05rem);
  }

  /* BRIDGE — special treatment */
  .section-block.is-bridge {
    background: rgba(200,169,110,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.1);
    padding: 2rem 2rem 2rem 2.5rem;
    margin-left: -1rem;
  }

  .section-block.is-bridge .lyric-line {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--warm);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  /* OUTRO */
  .section-block.is-outro .lyric-line {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.8vw, 1.15rem);
    line-height: 2.1;
    color: var(--ghost);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  /* TRACK INFO BAR */
  .track-bar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(14,12,10,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.12);
    padding: 0.9rem 6vw;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    transform: translateY(-100%);
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .track-bar.show {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .track-bar-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--paper);
  }

  .track-bar-meta {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--warm);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* PROGRESS LINE */
  .progress-bar {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--rust), var(--warm));
    z-index: 9998;
    width: 0%;
    transition: width 0.1s linear;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer {
    padding: 6vh 6vw 10vh;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .footer-brand {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--warm);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .footer-credit {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ash);
    line-height: 2;
    text-align: right;
  }

  /* SIDE RULE */
  .side-rule {
    position: fixed;
    left: 1.8vw;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    text-orientation: mixed;
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ash);
    opacity: 0.3;
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1100px) {
    .side-rule { display: block; }
  }

  /* SECTION COUNTER */
  .section-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--rust);
    opacity: 0.5;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-right: 0.6rem;
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero { padding: 0 5vw 7vh; }
    .lyrics-container { padding: 6vh 5vw; }
    .section-block.is-bridge { margin-left: 0; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .footer { flex-direction: column; }
    .footer-credit { text-align: left; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="progress-bar" id="progress"></div>

<div class="track-bar" id="trackBar">
  <span class="track-bar-title">Concrete Beats Clever</span>
  <span class="track-bar-meta">RyanrealAF · buildwhilebleeding.com</span>
</div>

<div class="side-rule">Concrete Beats Clever — RyanrealAF</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-alley-light"></div>

  <p class="label">RyanrealAF / Build While Bleeding</p>

  <h1 class="hero-title">
    <span class="title-stroke">Concrete</span>
    <span>Beats</span>
    <span>Clever</span>
  </h1>

  <div class="hero-tagline">Less talk, more help — that's love right now.</div>

  <div class="hero-byline">
    <div class="hero-byline-line"></div>
    <span class="hero-byline-text">Moody late-night boom-bap &nbsp;·&nbsp; Street romance &nbsp;·&nbsp; 87 BPM</span>
  </div>

  <div class="scroll-cue">
    <div class="scroll-dot"></div>
    <span class="scroll-text">Read the track</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SONIC BRIEF -->
<div class="sonic-brief">
  <div class="sonic-brief-inner">
    <p class="sonic-label">Sonic Direction</p>
    <p class="sonic-text">Moody, bouncy late-night boom-bap — low bass knock, cracked piano stabs, dusty drums, sharp front-facing rap vocals. Street romance with motion in the pocket.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- LYRICS -->
<main class="lyrics-container">

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <div class="section-block" data-section="intro">
    <div class="section-tag">
      <span class="section-num">01</span>
      <span class="section-tag-bracket">[ Intro ]</span>
      <span class="tag-pip"></span>
      <span class="section-tag-detail">Spoken, low &amp; smooth — cracked piano</span>
    </div>
    <div class="lyric-lines">
      <span class="lyric-line">Back alley glow</span>
      <span class="lyric-line adlib">(yeah)</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Gold on the grit</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">You by the SUV</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">I peeped the whole script</span>
      <span class="lyric-line adlib">(look)</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Stayed one step back</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Leaned in your wave</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">You cracked that silence</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">I let it behave</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VERSE 1 -->
  <div class="section-block" data-section="v1">
    <div class="section-tag">
      <span class="section-num">02</span>
      <span class="section-tag-bracket">[ Verse 1 ]</span>
      <span class="tag-pip"></span>
      <span class="section-tag-detail">Bouncy percussive cadence — heavy measured pocket</span>
    </div>
    <div class="lyric-lines">
      <span class="lyric-line">You by the hatchback, half-stacked, half-stressed</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Hands doing order while your head stay a mess</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Quick little moves, zip-zap, eyes on bright</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Like you trying line the whole world up right</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Then you start talking — easy, no force</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Voice got real glide, smooth in the course</span>
      <span class="lyric-line adlib">(right)</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Ain't jump thirsty, ain't press, ain't pry</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Just caught your tempo and I rode that vibe</span>
      <span class="lyric-gap"></span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Rich-side alley but the air felt rough</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Pretty little backdrop, life still tough</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Fresh paint hiding all the pressure and cracks</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Soft light landing, hard weight on your back</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">That beauty-plus-strain, that grace-plus-pain</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">That pretty face carrying the whole damn frame</span>
      <span class="lyric-line adlib">(mm)</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">So I stayed chill, let the whole thing breathe</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Some moments hit sweeter when you don't overreach</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HOOK 1 -->
  <div class="section-block is-hook" data-section="hook">
    <div class="section-tag">
      <span class="section-num">03</span>
      <span class="section-tag-bracket">[ Hook ]</span>
      <span class="tag-pip"></span>
      <span class="section-tag-detail">Slow, intimate — direct echoing</span>
    </div>
    <div class="lyric-lines">
      <span class="lyric-line">Less talk, more help, that's love right now</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Cold water in your hand, safe road out</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">I don't need forever, I just hold this down</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Concrete beats clever when the lights fade out</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Less talk, more help, that's love right now</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">No crowd, no noise, just a calm way out</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">You don't gotta answer what we are somehow</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Just tell me what helps right now</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VERSE 2 -->
  <div class="section-block" data-section="v2">
    <div class="section-tag">
      <span class="section-num">04</span>
      <span class="section-tag-bracket">[ Verse 2 ]</span>
      <span class="tag-pip"></span>
      <span class="section-tag-detail">Bouncy playful cadence — relaxed pocket</span>
    </div>
    <div class="lyric-lines">
      <span class="lyric-line">Then the day got live in a broke-folk way</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Curbside free piles lined up all day</span>
      <span class="lyric-line adlib">(ayy)</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Bent-ass lamp and a side-table leg</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">One milk crate, two blankets, something weird in a bag</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">SUV stuffed, jam-packed, no slack</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Still you yelling, "hold up, I can fit that in the back"</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Whole block looking like — what the hell is this?</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">You talking to a bookshelf like y'all got history and shit</span>
      <span class="lyric-gap"></span>
      <span class="lyric-line">And I can't lie, baby, you looked too good</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Wild little chaos in a rich folks hood</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">From the outside view we looked half insane</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Two tired souls in a slapstick frame</span>
      <span class="lyric-line adlib">(wait)</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Every odd little score, every curbside find</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Put a spark in your face and it eased your mind</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">So I ain't rush nothing, I let you cook</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Let you chase little treasures with that hungry look</span>
      <span class="lyric-gap"></span>
      <span class="lyric-line">No sigh in my chest, no drag in my tone</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">No "leave that there," no "come on, let's go"</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Cause every little find, every oddball score</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Put a spark in your face, had you laughing some more</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">And if peace came dressed like a lamp with no shade</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Load that bitch up, let the whole block gaze</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">If calm wore curb dust and a half-bent rack</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">I'd pop that trunk and help slide it in back</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HOOK 2 -->
  <div class="section-block is-hook" data-section="hook2">
    <div class="section-tag">
      <span class="section-num">05</span>
      <span class="section-tag-bracket">[ Hook ]</span>
    </div>
    <div class="lyric-lines">
      <span class="lyric-line">Less talk, more help, that's love right now</span>
