      <span class="lyric-line">Less talk, more help, that's love right now</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">No crowd, no noise, just a calm way out</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">You don't gotta answer what we are somehow</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Just tell me what helps right now</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VERSE 3 -->
  <div class="section-block" data-section="v3">
    <div class="section-tag">
      <span class="section-num">06</span>
      <span class="section-tag-bracket">[ Verse 3 ]</span>
      <span class="tag-pip"></span>
      <span class="section-tag-detail">Intimate bounce as night falls — measured &amp; heavy</span>
    </div>
    <div class="lyric-lines">
      <span class="lyric-line">Then the light dipped low, blue slid on gold</span>
      <span class="lyric-line">Street got quiet, night got bold</span>
      <span class="lyric-line adlib">(yeah)<
